milestones.description: Lefebvre and Scholte's 28-run partnership is NED's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between Esmeijer and Schiferli
Lefebvre and Adeel Raja's 23-run partnership is NED's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 6 between Bakker and Robert van Oosterom
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
This is the lowest match aggregate (278) involving teams Pakistan & Netherlands in ODIs
